The '''Oil Refinery''' converts raw [[en/Manual/Base Set/Economy/Oil]] into [[en/Manual/Base Set/Economy/Goods]].

It can only be positioned near the edges of a map, even when using [[en/Manual/Base Set/Economy/Industries|Fund New Industry]]. This is due to a [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Oil refinery limit|setting in openttd.cfg]].

Oil Refineries can be destroyed by the [[en/Disaster#Oil_refinery_explosion|military jet disaster]], but will rebuild itself soon.

